$[amount] payment for [Product].

[Update Payment Method →]

Takes less than 30 seconds. Your [data/projects/team access]
is safe, but we'll need a valid payment method to keep your
account active.

Questions? Reply here and we'll help.

— [Product] Team
""" ;
